    "name": "Dream Cage",
    "steam_appid": 3122170,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122170/extras/b0e3e6e8e9c4056d94cf7c87b9213e6b.avif?t=1746970381\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >五个独特的恶魔将困扰你，每个恶魔都有独特的设计和动画。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验基于真实故事的五夜睡眠瘫痪。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的麦克风捕捉每一个声音——你能生还并解开谜团吗？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到25个以上的异常，揭示睡眠瘫痪的起源。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两个结局，但只有一个揭示了终极真相。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记忆丧失会导致分心——找到药丸恢复正常功能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在寻找异常的过程中面对随机的鬼魂现象——你能保持专注吗？</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122170/extras/a40ced6f85011903500b2e3c469e9d15.poster.avif?t=1746970381\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122170/extras/a40ced6f85011903500b2e3c469e9d15.webm?t=1746970381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122170/extras/a40ced6f85011903500b2e3c469e9d15.mp4?t=1746970381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >体验睡眠瘫痪</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于与经历过睡眠瘫痪的人们的对话，我们努力忠实地再现他们的感受和所见。我们将这些故事转化为我们自己的愿景，从真实经历中汲取灵感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >熬过五个夜晚，每个夜晚都将让你面对一个精心设计的独特实体，它将对你发起挑战。记住，要活过这五个夜晚并揭开罗伯特噩梦的源头，你必须保持安静——不要尖叫或发出任何声音。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122170/extras/fce5db6d804ba74e30157505758996ba.poster.avif?t=1746970381\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122170/extras/fce5db6d804ba74e30157505758996ba.webm?t=1746970381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122170/extras/fce5db6d804ba74e30157505758996ba.mp4?t=1746970381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >异常现象将指引你</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现年50岁的罗伯特多年来一直饱受记忆问题和失眠的困扰。由于药物成瘾，他有时无法分清现实与幻觉。但真正的问题是——这真的只是幻觉吗？还是在表面之下隐藏着什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到超过25个异常现象，以揭示真相和罗伯特问题的根源。只有发现所有异常，你才能解锁真正的结局并揭示完整的故事。然而，不要被挑战表面的简单性所迷惑。罗伯特的内心隐藏着许多秘密，而正是这些谜团让你的任务变得更加困难。</p>",
